creator: Joanna Baillie
description:
LibriVox recording of The Kitten by Joanna Baillie.

Read in English by Greg Giordano; Jason Mills; Jeanie; Leonard Wilson; MaryAnn Spiegel; Rosslyn Carlyle; and by Rachel and SuperCoconut.

Librivox volunteers bring you seven readings of The Kitten by Joanna Baillee. This is the fortnightly poetry project for October 26, 2014.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (23MB)
